---
layout: base.njk
title: Workout Reports
description: Recent workout data and analysis
breadcrumb:
  - label: Horses
    url: /horses/
  - label: Workout Reports
---

<div class="page-header">
  <h1>Workout Reports</h1>
  <p class="subtitle">Recent workout times, analysis, and notes</p>
</div>

<div class="content-body">
  <p>Below are the most recent workout reports for horses in training. Workouts are tracked at Oaklawn Park and other training facilities.</p>
</div>

{% dataTable workouts, ["date", "horse", "track", "distance", "time", "notes"] %}

<div class="content-body">
  <h2>Workout Reports Archive</h2>
  {% set reports = collections.workoutReports %}
  {% if reports.length > 0 %}
    <ul>
    {% for report in reports %}
      <li><a href="{{ report.url }}">{{ report.data.title }}</a> — {{ report.data.date | dateFormat }}</li>
    {% endfor %}
    </ul>
  {% else %}
    <p>Detailed reports coming soon.</p>
  {% endif %}
</div>
